data.description: An amazing lake community home in one of the most sought after neighborhoods in Lake Wylie. This home boasts an expansive first level including an open foyer with a striking staircase, formal dining room and open gathering room with a fireplace. The chef's kitchen features gorgeous white kitchen cabinets and quartz countertops. The kitchen also features a large island farmhouse sink, stainless steel appliances including  double wall oven and a 5 burner gas cook top. The kitchen adjacent family room features a custom built wall unit containing spacious shelving and storage and 2 separate workstations. Off of the kitchen you will find a covered outdoor living space that opens to a spacious fenced back yard that also contains a raised vegetable & flower bed. The second floor features the primary suite with a luxurious ensuite. Also featured on the second floor are 3 secondary bedrooms and 2 additional baths.
